{"tid":1149078,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"展現統領宇宙中国夢獲當局好評　毛澤東佛祖殿香火旺盛","createTime":"2019-05-11T01:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T02:13:49.000Z","uid":184679,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"659b9ebfa89a68fd762156661563e4ac06f37e1d","tid":1149078,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T01:54:53.000Z","msg":"在中共持續不減的「滅佛」行動中，各地無論是大型宗教造像，還是名剎古寺，都陸續被查封、拆毀，就當下中共「見佛就拆」的背景下，河南有一座無宗教活動場所登記證的廟宇不但沒遭打壓，反而還被當地宗教局批為紅色愛國主義教育基地，香火旺盛。這座與眾不同的廟宇就是「毛主席佛祖殿」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bitterwintertw.b-cdn.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/%E2%80%9C%E6%AF%9B%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E4%BD%9B%E7%A5%96%E6%AE%BF%E2%80%9D%E5%A4%96%E8%A7%82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbitterwintertw.b-cdn.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F%25E2%2580%259C%25E6%25AF%259B%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BD%259B%25E7%25A5%2596%25E6%25AE%25BF%25E2%2580%259D%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25A7%2582.jpg&h=457940f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「毛主席佛祖殿」外觀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bitterwintertw.b-cdn.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/%E6%AF%9B%E6%B3%BD%E4%B8%9C%E9%9C%B2%E5%A4%A9%E9%9B%95%E5%83%8F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbitterwintertw.b-cdn.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F%25E6%25AF%259B%25E6%25B3%25BD%25E4%25B8%259C%25E9%259C%25B2%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E9%259B%2595%25E5%2583%258F.jpg&h=6153eb03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n毛澤東露天雕像<br />\n<br />\n「毛主席佛祖殿」位於汝州市寄料鎮張坡村西約2公里處的青龍山上（原名西坡，建廟後改名青龍山）。該廟的大門兩側以及廟頂的最高處各插一面國旗，大門兩旁有兩個騎馬大將軍，左邊是華國鋒（毛澤東指定的接班人，前中共領導人之一），右邊是董必武（中共開國元勳之一）。儼然是一處共產黨的紀念館。<br />\n<br />\n進入大院，一座大型露天毛澤東雕像赫然在目，雕像的底座上雕刻有將毛神化為「佛祖」的詩句，稱「毛主就是新玉皇，統天統地統人間」，將來道教、佛教等都歸到毛澤東這一教。這似乎影射了共產黨長期鎮壓宗教自由並企圖稱霸世界的野心目的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bitterwintertw.b-cdn.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/%E5%B0%86%E6%AF%9B%E7%A5%9E%E5%8C%96%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%9B%E7%A5%96%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%97%E5%8F%A5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbitterwintertw.b-cdn.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F%25E5%25B0%2586%25E6%25AF%259B%25E7%25A5%259E%25E5%258C%2596%25E4%25B8%25BA%25E4%25BD%259B%25E7%25A5%2596%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25AF%2597%25E5%258F%25A5.jpg&h=1561c66b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將毛神化為佛祖的詩句<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bitterwintertw.b-cdn.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/%E5%A5%87%E8%91%A9%E5%85%AB%E5%8D%A6%E5%80%92%E8%BD%AC%E4%B9%BE%E5%9D%A4%E4%B8%89%E8%89%B2%E9%B1%BC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbitterwintertw.b-cdn.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F%25E5%25A5%2587%25E8%2591%25A9%25E5%2585%25AB%25E5%258D%25A6%25E5%2580%2592%25E8%25BD%25AC%25E4%25B9%25BE%25E5%259D%25A4%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%2589%25B2%25E9%25B1%25BC.jpg&h=8135bc3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n奇葩八卦倒轉乾坤三色魚圖<br />\n<br />\n更為怪誕的是，該廟院內地面上繪有一副被稱為八卦倒轉乾坤三色魚圖。八卦圖原為黑白兩色，代表陰陽兩方，現在卻變成了黑白黃三色，中間還多出了一個紅圈。據一女信徒解釋說，這個圈代表毛澤東就是紅太陽。<br />\n<br />\n這座廟共兩層，一樓正殿名為皇府殿，二樓正殿名為佛祖金殿，毛澤東的塑像被封為「宇宙天尊佛祖」置於正中間，在毛澤東塑像左右兩邊分別是中天大佛周恩來和貫天大佛朱德的塑像。兩邊牆上還掛著中共開國十大元帥彭德懷等人的照片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bitterwintertw.b-cdn.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/%E6%AF%9B%E6%B3%BD%E4%B8%9C%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%B6%E5%B4%87%E6%8B%9C%E8%80%85%E5%B0%81%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E5%AE%87%E5%AE%99%E5%A4%A9%E5%B0%8A%E4%BD%9B%E7%A5%96%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E5%B7%A6%E5%8F%B3%E4%B8%A4%E8%BE%B9%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%B1%E5%BE%B7%E5%92%8C%E5%91%A8%E6%81%A9%E6%9D%A5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbitterwintertw.b-cdn.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F%25E6%25AF%259B%25E6%25B3%25BD%25E4%25B8%259C%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2585%25B6%25E5%25B4%2587%25E6%258B%259C%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25B0%2581%25E4%25B8%25BA%25E2%2580%259C%25E5%25AE%2587%25E5%25AE%2599%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%25B0%258A%25E4%25BD%259B%25E7%25A5%2596%25E2%2580%259D%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%25B7%25A6%25E5%258F%25B3%25E4%25B8%25A4%25E8%25BE%25B9%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%259C%25B1%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%2581%25A9%25E6%259D%25A5.jpg&h=31446d41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n毛澤東被封為「宇宙天尊佛祖」，左右兩邊是朱德和周恩來<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bitterwintertw.b-cdn.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/%E6%AE%BF%E5%86%85%E7%9A%84%E5%A2%99%E4%B8%8A%E6%8C%82%E7%9D%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E5%BC%80%E5%9B%BD%E5%8D%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%83%E5%B8%85%E7%9A%84%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbitterwintertw.b-cdn.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F%25E6%25AE%25BF%25E5%2586%2585%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A2%2599%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%258C%2582%25E7%259D%2580%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%25BC%2580%25E5%259B%25BD%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%25B8%2585%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%2585%25A7%25E7%2589%2587.jpg&h=cb09ea91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n殿內的牆上掛著中共開國十大元帥的照片<br />\n<br />\n每逢燒香日，與中國目前許多寺廟被毀、僧尼凋零的現況相比，這座毛主席佛祖殿十分熱鬧，燒香磕頭的「信徒」很多。4月7日，洛陽市欒川縣前檢查院副院長也前來上香磕頭。據廟內工作人員透露，自該廟建成以來，各省都有信徒來燒香叩拜，包括來自河南省的一位公安廳廳長。一位來自北京的科學家來燒香時還透露，「習主席也信神，中央領導人也燒香磕頭。」<br />\n<br />\n一村民說：「毛澤東明明是個人，還是個無神論者，文革時期號召掃除一切牛鬼蛇神，現在居然有人把他當成佛祖拜，真是稀奇古怪！」<br />\n<br />\n事實上在中國民間，長期以來把毛澤東「神化」的大有人在，獨立中國問題學者胡星斗教授曾在接受美國之音採訪時批評稱，「毛澤東熱」類似於反人類、反文明的義和團和塔利班思潮 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bitterwintertw.b-cdn.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/%E7%BA%A2%E8%89%B2%E7%88%B1%E5%9B%BD%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E7%89%8C%E5%AD%90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbitterwintertw.b-cdn.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F%25E7%25BA%25A2%25E8%2589%25B2%25E7%2588%25B1%25E5%259B%25BD%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E4%25B9%2589%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%259F%25BA%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%2589%258C%25E5%25AD%2590.jpg&h=96080e16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅色愛國主義教育基地的牌子<br />\n<br />\n對於這座「毛主席佛祖殿」的存在，當地有佛教徒直言不諱地表示，把毛澤東當佛拜，是對佛祖的褻瀆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.bitterwinter.org/mao-zedong-temple-showed-ccps-ambition-lead-universe/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.bitterwinter.org%2Fmao-zedong-temple-showed-ccps-ambition-lead-universe%2F&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUDaf%2B7McJKZiP%2F5rhSwlYLA%3D&h=da315027\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.bitterwinter.org/mao-zedong-temple-showed-ccps-ambition-lead-universe/</a>"},{"pid":"7664a6df0c554b2687f70067e4ddac2f02dfd941","tid":1149078,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T01:56:44.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdeeb020d15820960501e7d5b927e79e30918924","tid":1149078,"uid":178236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T02:01:32.000Z","msg":"起果個搵到食。仲唔fat fat"},{"pid":"4e9c24283eca7e251500c89cb13cdb733407e593","tid":1149078,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T04:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b47268d2bb6f51e70e27677b8bdfb25d4a9f930","tid":1149078,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T04:29:21.000Z","msg":"以為係老衲開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd249de46781a3bb6537c6152d7ecebf208a4ffa","tid":1149078,"uid":93986,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g8b6ZzE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8b6ZzE.png&h=323947e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S18dEzE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS18dEzE.png&h=27ed8a4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aae50361b64f857e1c6af620a843e9079183d5dd","tid":1149078,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd249de46781a3bb6537c6152d7ecebf208a4ffa","tid":1149078,"uid":93986,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g8b6ZzE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8b6ZzE.png&h=32394