" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講好打林標，賀龍都好打過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20fd921725579e680540bb270e90e6688480b281","tid":1149078,"uid":243175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:36:11.000Z","msg":"曲線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1451a3a359887da20f108a0c3fecf5acb018cbc7","tid":1149078,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:36:56.000Z","msg":"cap水"},{"pid":"ecdd279235cf478a7ff446ceb2724f0bbe43730d","tid":1149078,"uid":63887,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"aae50361b64f857e1c6af620a843e9079183d5dd","tid":1149078,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd249de46781a3bb6537c6152d7ecebf208a4ffa","tid":1149078,"uid":93986,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g8b6ZzE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8b6ZzE.png&h=323947e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S18dEzE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS18dEzE.png&h=27ed8a4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:15:42.000Z","msg":"原來尾田向毛魔取經"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:13:49.000Z","msg":"中間喺赤犬，尾田今次大獲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}